# UrbanPulse Frontend — Vite Environment Variables
# These VITE_ prefixed vars are injected at build time and safe to expose
# (they use the PUBLIC anon key, not the service-role key)

# Fill in after creating your Supabase project:
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-public-key
